About Us
Downtown Business Association of Stuart, Inc.
Our Mission Statement:
To provide a cohesive vision and an action plan for sustainability and future growth of business in Historic Downtown Stuart and the surrounding areas.
Our Primary Goal:
To market and promote the businesses in the Historic Downtown District and the surrounding areas.
What We Do:
We promote the unique history of Stuart by supporting Stuart Heritage Museum.
The DBA plans events downtown with our events committee and in cooperation with the City and Stuart Main Street.
We promote “positives” about downtown, and the surrounding areas and encourage shoppers that we are an alternative to boring & “cookie cutter” mall shopping.
The DBA, as a body of business people has a collective voice with City government, which is regarded as influential. We provide a platform through which to air grievances and concerns.
Welcome to Historic Downtown Stuart. Please browse around the website to find all that downtown has to offer. Check back frequently as we will be updating the site to keep you informed. If you have any questions, comments, or complaints, feel free to send us an email located on the contact us page. Thank you.
